snippet.title: Bip Bop 3 (1993, MS-DOS) - Full Longplay [720p60]
snippet.description:
Special shoutout to Accursed Farms for making the full series accessible to everyone.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R-JAICJ0k4Q

Pretty much extended version of Bip Bop II, with more quirky features (teleporting balls!) and more story to make the trilogy worthwhile.

13:40 - getting the ball wedged = win.
————————————————————————————
Bip Bop 1 — https://youtu.be/2esCC-c6Ql8
Bip Bop 2 — https://youtu.be/HNsGJthNEYg
Bip Bop 3 — You are here
